Usage: selectPGPin [-help] [-all] [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}]
                   [-layer <layer> | {list_of_layer}] [-net <name>]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-all                                 # Specifies whether to select all PG pins
                                     # (bool, optional)
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}                  # Specifies the coordinates of the area
                                     # (box, optional)
-layer <layer> | {list_of_layer}     # Specifies layers (string, optional)
-net <name>                          # Specifies net name ((net)+, optional)